        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"thumbs up\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f44d\" role=\"img\" title=\"thumbs up\">:thumbs_up:</span> alexcrichton submitted <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13345#pullrequestreview-4292584659\">PR review</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Everything here looks reasonable to me, but I also get tangled up in the futures here. CI looks like it's failing also on a channel/future-related thing which seems like it might be either a preexisting race or one accidentally introduced here?</p>\n</blockquote>",
