        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"speech balloon\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f4ac\" role=\"img\" title=\"speech balloon\">:speech_balloon:</span> alexcrichton created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13345#discussion_r3243579575\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>It's ok to drop the mention of the old code here, no need to document what-once-was and I think the first part of these docs stand well on their own</p>\n</blockquote>",
